duck: "Complicated" (Rihanna song) - "Complicated" is a song by Barbadian recording artist Rihanna from her fifth studio album Loud (2010).
complicated definition: consisting of parts intricately combined.
"Complicated" (Carolyn Dawn Johnson song) - "Complicated" is the title of a song co-written and recorded by Canadian country music singer Carolyn Dawn Johnson.
"Complicated" (Avril Lavigne song) - "Complicated" is a song by Avril Lavigne and was her debut single, released in 2002 from her debut album, Let Go.
Complicated (Tanya Tucker album), or the title song
"Complicated" (The Cliks song) - "Complicated" is the third single from The Cliks' debut studio album, Snakehouse.
